31
00:11:13,281 --> 00:11:19,996
- Name?
- Hayes. H-A-Y-E-S.

32
00:13:00,939 --> 00:13:06,100
Howdy, Billy.
How are you doing? Okay?

33
00:13:08,488 --> 00:13:14,942
