65
00:21:32,112 --> 00:21:37,107
Will it ease the pain,
the shame you must be feeling?

66
00:21:37,284 --> 00:21:40,699
Forgive me, please.

67
00:21:55,970 --> 00:21:59,220
Could I have a blanket?

68
00:21:59,390 --> 00:22:02,890
