86
00:26:51,579 --> 00:26:56,158
Thanks. I'm Billy Hayes...
at least I used to be.

87
00:27:34,625 --> 00:27:38,789
- Why peacocks?
- They use them instead of dogs.

88
00:27:38,963 --> 00:27:45,630
They scream like mad if they're
disturbed and they don't get rabies.

89
00:27:46,721 --> 00:27:52,013
- Who are the kids?
- Little fuckers...

90
00:27:52,186 --> 00:27:56,765
Thieves, rapists, murderers...
You name it, they do it.

91
00:27:56,941 --> 00:28:01,021
Don't trust any of them.
They tell Rifki everything.

92
00:28:01,195 --> 00:28:04,481
He's the squeal around here.
He sells tea, -

93
00:28:04,657 --> 00:28:08,441
- hash, blankets,
