120
00:30:36,653 --> 00:30:40,734
There's no straight lawyers
in Turkey.

121
00:30:40,908 --> 00:30:44,527
They're all bent.

122
00:30:44,704 --> 00:30:49,995
Bent as hairpins.
Occupational necessity.

123
00:30:50,168 --> 00:30:54,961
They have special classes
in corruption at night school.

124
00:30:56,342 --> 00:31:00,174
If you're suspected of honesty,
you're disbarred.

125
00:31:05,308 --> 00:31:09,853
I knew a lawyer fellow once.

126
00:31:10,023 --> 00:31:14,686
He got that Frenchman off.
La Roche.

127
00:31:18,031 --> 00:31:21,151
A big smuggler.

128
00:31:21,326 --> 00:31:24,660
200 kilos.

129
00:31:26,082 --> 00:31:30,791
He put enough bread
in enough pockets. Got bail.

130
00:31:30,962 --> 00:31:34,580
Vanished.

131
00:31:34,758 --> 00:31:39,634
- His name?
- Who?

132
00:31:39,805 --> 00:31:45,226
- The lawyer.
- Lawyer?

133
00:31:45,393 --> 00:31:50,103
Who got the Frenchman off.

134
00:31:51,984 --> 00:31:57,821
Yesil is his name.

135
00:31:59,701 --> 00:32:03,699
I don't know anything else
about him.

136
00:32:03,872 --> 00:32:07,289
Yesil.

137
00:32:09,170 --> 00:32:14,164
The best thing to do
is get your ass out of here.

138
00:32:14,341 --> 00:32:18,754
- Yeah, but how?
- Catch the midnight express.

139
00:32:18,930 --> 00:32:22,097
Whas that?

140
00:32:24,727 --> 00:32:33,817
Is not a train.
Is a prison word for... escape.

141
00:32:38,492 --> 00:32:41,577
It doesn't stop around here.

142
00:33:28,588 --> 00:33:31,506
Dad, I'm sorry.

143
00:33:31,675 --> 00:33:34,878
Forget it.

144
00:33:35,053 --> 00:33:41,852
I'll punch you in the nose later.
We've got to get you out of here.

145
00:33:42,020 --> 00:33:46,728
This is a suit I brought for you.

146
00:33:47,984 --> 00:33:51,519
Smarten you up a little.

147
00:33:54,575 --> 00:33:58,785
- Are you all right?
- Yeah.

148
00:33:58,953 --> 00:34:02,323
How's Mom?

149
00:34:02,499 --> 00:34:06,498
Well, she's bad.

150
00:34:06,671 --> 00:34:11,498
